Opening screen to press play or view instructions (buttons)
Show twenty cards on screen (10 pairs) that are randomly shuffled
cards are imported images to java
Three levels means different number of cards
First level: 10 cards
Second level: 20 cards??
Third Level: 22 cards??
User has to try and match and all the pairs
Time limit of 2 minutes to match all the cards
If user does not pass the level (surpasses the two minutes), they do not move onto the next level
They have the option of either restarting the current level or closing the game
If user does pass all levels, they will have the option of closing the screen or restarting the whole game
